Snowflake Internal — Enablement Asset
=====================================

Copyright (c) Snowflake Inc. All rights reserved.

This repository is an INTERNAL Snowflake enablement asset. It is intended for
use by Snowflake employees to explore, demonstrate, and discuss data ontologies
with customers.

- It is NOT open-source and carries no open-source license.
- Do NOT distribute this repository, or copies of it, outside of Snowflake.
- Do NOT publish it to a public repository, package registry, or website.
- Sharing with customers should be done through approved channels (e.g. a guided
  demo, or code walked through in a session) rather than by handing over the repo.

The data in this repository is entirely synthetic. It contains no real patient,
member, provider, or claims information, and must not be replaced with real PHI
or PII.

Questions about appropriate use: contact the repository owner.
